	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod proxime de transitu <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p17907">Gonzagae</persName> permisso scripsi, ea conditione interea factum intellexi, ut sine omni armatura bellioque apparatu, si velit, transeat, id quod cum ipse nolit, alia via exercitum deducet in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l20">Inferiorem Germaniam</placeName>, per vallem scilicet Athesinam.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepimus quoque interea ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> literas, quibus significatur <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p19065">Ioannem Friderychum</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonię</placeName> ducem 3. martii e vivis excessisse simulque 9 diebus ante ipsum obiisse uxorem suam.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Obiit quoque <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name">Arnoldus</persName> ille, ducis <persName ref="p8105" cert="high">Ottonis Heinrychi</persName> quaestor, quem nosti.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alias ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> nihil habemus, nisi quod de comitiis a Caesare indictis scribunt, quae tamen non futura sperant.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es sol hertzog <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1546" cert="high">Christoff von Wirtenberg</persName> imm anfang diß monats ußgezogen sin für <placeName ref="l1426" cert="high">Hohen-Rechberg</placeName>, das schloß, von wegen das imm derselbig edelman, <persName type="auto_name">Uͦtz von Rechberg</persName> genannt, zwen puren erstochen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l361" cert="high">Nürenbergischen</placeName> söllend auch noch vor <placeName type="auto_name">Blasenburg</placeName> ligen, <placeName type="auto_name">Ruchenpalm</placeName> eroberet haben, deß kriegens muͤd sin und deß marggrafen halb in großen sorgen ston.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Zuͦ <placeName ref="l513" cert="high">Ulm</placeName> hatt man wider ein predicanten, der gar lutherisch, und halt man in einer kirchen 3 religiones nacheinander.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Diß schript <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5355" cert="high">Onoffrius Hürus</persName> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055">Blaurero</persName>, der selb da gwesen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Idem de <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> multa et plausibilia, sed non admodum certa.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916">Schertlinum</persName> Caesari quidem reconciliatum, nondum vero <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName> regi, id quod diversum est ab eo, quid hic de illo fuit sparsum; <foreign xml:lang="de">hatt ein predicanten widerumb gen <placeName ref="l76" cert="high">Burtenbach</placeName>, da sin herrschafft ist, gesetzt.</foreign></s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec quoniam ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> partim, partim a Blaurero accepimus, volui tibi quoque communicare, quamvis haec ipsa et multa alia et certiora te habere existimem.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie lecti sunt senatores novi 3, inter quos <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3544" cert="high">Wolphgangus ab Erlach</persName> fratri <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3530" cert="high">Ioanni Rodolpho</persName> successit, quem etiam (non dubito) prudentia superabit, humanitate certe nunc antecellit longe.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutat te quęstor <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8012">Hallerus</persName>, <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> noster et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2919">Schlatterus</persName>, simul quoque uxor mea; salvi sint omnes tui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Bene vale.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 28. martii.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Fratri meo nihil scribo; salutabis illum ex me et ex his, quę videbuntur, poteris communicare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Hallerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae fidelissimo pastori, domino et compatri suo charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingeren</persName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
